        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Her ideas on life in general had been acquired through the medium of popular respectable novel writers, and modified or emphasised by such knowledge as her aunt, the vicar, and her aunt's housekeeper had put at her disposal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
