        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "And now, in her twenty ninth year, her aunt's death had left her, well provided for as regards income, but somewhat isolated in the matter of kith and kin and human companionship.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "She could hardly remember ever having met them, but once or twice in the course of the last three or four years they had expressed a polite wish that she should pay them a visit; they had probably not been unduly depressed by the fact that her aunt's failing health had prevented her from accepting their invitation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000005_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000005_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "mrs Bludward was something of an invalid, and Robert was a young man who had been at Oxford and was going into Parliament.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Further than that Alethia's information did not go; her imagination, founded on her extensive knowledge of the people one met in novels, had to supply the gaps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000005_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000005_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Robert was more of a problem.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000005_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000005_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "It was probable, Alethia considered, that Robert came into the last category, in which case she was certain to enjoy the companionship of one or two excellent women, and might possibly catch glimpses of undesirable adventuresses or come face to face with reckless admiration seeking married women.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "The train which carried Alethia towards her destination was a local one, with the wayside station habit strongly developed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "There was a certain scornful ring in his question.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Robert Bludward?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "An out an'-out rotter, that's what he is.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Ought to be ashamed to look any decent man in the face.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Send him to Parliament to represent us-not much!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Tells a pack of lies to get our votes, that's all that he's after, damn him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Properly exposed him, hip and thigh, I tell you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"He was hissed down at Shoalford yesterday,\" said one of the speakers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Had it come to that?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "There was something dramatically biblical in the idea of Robert Bludward's neighbours and acquaintances hissing him for very scorn.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000013_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000013_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "In placid Saxon blooded England people did not demonstrate their feelings lightly and without some strong compelling cause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "What manner of evildoer was Robert Bludward?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "The train stopped at another small station, and the two men got out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Alethia pounced on it, in the expectation of finding a cultured literary endorsement of the censure which these rough farming men had expressed in their homely, honest way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "She had not far to look; \"mr",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Robert Bludward, Swanker,\" was the title of one of the principal articles in the paper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "And this monster was going to meet her at Derrelton Station in a few short minutes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "She would know him at once; he would have the dark beetling brows, the quick, furtive glance, the sneering, unsavoury smile that always characterised the Sir Jaspers of this world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "It was too late to escape; she must force herself to meet him with outward calm.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "It was a considerable shock to her to find that Robert was fair, with a snub nose, merry eye, and rather a schoolboy manner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"A serpent in duckling's plumage,\" was her private comment; merciful chance had revealed him to her in his true colours.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "As they drove away from the station a dissipated looking man of the labouring class waved his hat in friendly salute.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Good luck to you, mr Bludward,\" he shouted; \"you'll come out on top!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "We'll break old Chobham's neck for him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Who was that man?\" asked Alethia quickly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Oh, one of my supporters,\" laughed Robert; \"a bit of a poacher and a bit of a pub loafer, but he's on the right side.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "So these were the sort of associates that Robert Bludward consorted with, thought Alethia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Who is the person he referred to as old Chobham?\" she asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "So there was an upright man, possibly a very Hugo in character, who was thwarting and defying the evildoer in his nefarious career, and there was a dastardly plot afoot to break his neck!",
