    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "He had the frank open countenance, neatly brushed hair and tidy clothes that betoken a clear conscience and a good mother.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "He stared straight at the occupants of the car, and, after he had passed them, sang in his clear, boyish voice:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Robert merely laughed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "He had goaded them to desperation with his shameless depravity till they spoke openly of putting him to a violent death, and he laughed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "From her no help was to be expected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "After breakfast Alethia, on the pretext of going to look at an outlying rose garden, slipped away to the village through which they had passed on the previous evening.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000027_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000027_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Suddenly she started, and began to read with breathless attention a prominently printed article, headed \"A Little Limelight on Sir john Chobham.\" The colour ebbed away from her face, a look of frightened despair crept into her eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000027_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000027_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Sir john, the Hugo of her imagination, was, if anything, rather more depraved and despicable than Robert Bludward.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000027_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000027_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "He was also a candidate for Parliament, it seemed, and as there was only one seat in this particular locality, it was obvious that the success of either Robert or Sir john would mean a check to the ambitions of the other, hence, no doubt, the rivalry and enmity between these otherwise kindred souls.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000027_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000027_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "One was seeking to have his enemy done to death, the other was apparently trying to stir up his supporters to an act of \"Lynch law\".",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"I must go back to Webblehinton at once,\" Alethia informed her astonished hostess at lunch time; \"I have had a telegram.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "A friend is very seriously ill and I have been sent for.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "It was dreadful to have to concoct lies, but it would be more dreadful to have to spend another night under that roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "She had come unscathed through it, but what might have happened if she had gone unsuspectingly to visit Sir john Chobham and warn him of his danger?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_2327_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/2327/7085_2327_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "What indeed!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "When it was the Six Hundred and Ninth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Then Judar sat watching and after awhile, his feet appeared above the water and the fisher said, \"He is dead and damned!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000001_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000001_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Whither went they?\" enquired the Moor, and Judar replied, \"I pinioned their hands behind them and cast them into the lake, where they were drowned, and the same fate is in store for thee.\" The Moor laughed and rejoined, saying, \"O unhappy!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000001_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000001_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Then he waited awhile; presently the Moor thrust both hands forth of the water and called out to him, saying, \"Ho, good fellow, cast out thy net!\" So Judar threw the net over him and drew him ashore, and lo! in each hand he held a fish as red as coral.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000001_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000001_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Quoth the Moor, \"Bring me the two caskets that are in the saddle bags.\" So Judar brought them and opened them to him, and he laid in each casket a fish and shut them up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000001_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000001_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Then he pressed Judar to his bosom and kissed him on the right cheek and the left, saying, \"Allah save thee from all stress!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "When it was the Six Hundred and Tenth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Our father was wont to make use of this book, of which we had some small matter by heart, and each of us desired to possess it, that he might acquaint himself with what was therein.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "As for the brand, if its bearer draw it and brandish it against an army, the army will be put to the rout; and if he say the while, 'Slay yonder host,' there will come forth of that sword lightning and fire, that will kill the whole many.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "When it was the Six Hundred and Eleventh Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75807_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75807/7085_75807_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "\"Nay,\" answered the Maghribi, \"they are Ifrits in the guise of fish.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "When it was the Six Hundred and Seventeenth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "If ye allow me aught to clothe me, 'twill be of your bounty, and each of you shall traffic with the folk for himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Ye are my sons and I am your mother; wherefore let us abide as we are, lest your brother come back and we be disgraced.\" But they accepted not her words and passed the night, wrangling with each other.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "So he looked out and listening, heard all the angry words that passed between them and saw the division of the spoil.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000001_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000001_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "After awhile, his master the merchant set out on a pilgrimage to Meccah, taking Judar with him, and when they reached the city, the Cairene repaired to the Haram temple, to circumambulate the Ka'abah.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "When it was the Six Hundred and Eighteenth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000003_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000003_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "They swooned away for excess of fear, and when they recovered, they found themselves in their mother's house and saw Judar seated by her side.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000003_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000003_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Quoth he, \"I salute you, O my brothers! you have cheered me by your presence.\" And they bowed their heads and burst into tears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000003_000012",
