        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "She continued, It hath reached me, O auspicious King, that Judar said to his brothers, \"How could you do with me thus?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000005_000001",
