        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "But repent unto Allah and crave pardon of Him, and He will forgive you both, for He is the Most Forgiving, the Merciful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "As for me, I pardon you and welcome you: no harm shall befall you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Then Judar brought forth food and they ate and took their ease and lay down to sleep.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
