        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Meanwhile, Al Ra'ad summoned his attendant Jinn and bade them build the palace.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7085_75810_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7085/75810/7085_75810_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Judar was delighted with it while he was passing along the highway and withal it had cost him nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
