        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7085",
        "content": "Moreover, he sent other four score, who fetched comely black girls, and forty others brought male chattels and carried them all to Judar's house, which they filled.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
